 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - London muggings rise despite £13m Operation Eagle Eye campaign  </TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>London muggings rise despite £13m Operation Eagle Eye campaign  </b><br><br><br><b><h2>  19 July 1996</h2></b><br><h2> London muggings rise despite £13m campaign</h2><h3>Figures show 69 per cent of street robbery arrests were young black men  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Alan Travis</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>Scotland Yard's &#163;13m Operation Eagle Eye campaign against  street robbers has had only a limited impact in its first year, according to the Metropolitan police annual report published yesterday.  <p>  <p>The official London crime figures show there were 4,000 more street robberies, a rise of 14 per cent, in the year to the end of March 1996. The campaign, launched in August last year, drew strong criticism because it appeared to be targeted mainly at young black men.  <p>  <p>But the commissioner, Sir Paul Condon, yesterday defended it, saying it had capped the increase in snatch thefts and robberies of personal property which had been increasing by 20 to 30 per cent a year. He cited figures showing street muggings had fallen between November 1995 and June 1996 by some five per cent. Detections also doubled, to 19 per cent of street robberies being cleared up.  <p>  <p>"Not only have we capped street robbery, but we are bringing it down dramatically," he said. Police figures show that 69 per cent of those arrested for street robberies as a result of Operation Eagle Eye have been young black men. After the launch of the operation, Sir Paul said that in some parts of London most muggers were black.  <p>  <p>He also gave a fillip to those seeking to reform the law on prostitution, when he advocated relaxing the definition of a brothel to allow two women to work together from private premises so they could offer each other mutual protection. At present it is only legal for one woman to work as a prostitute from private premises. He is the most senior police officer to advocate reform of prostitution laws.  <p>  <p>He also said he wanted to see kerb crawling made an arrestable offence to reduce nuisance to local residents. "I am not convinced licensed brothels would help, they would probably create no-go areas. But I favour a more pragmatic approach."  <p>  <p>The overall crime figures for London show only a slight drop of 1,000, to 822,596 recorded offences. Burglaries were up by 9,000, to 170,000, but that was attributed more to a change in recording methods than an increase in break-ins. Sir Paul said the last three years had seen a 20 per cent fall in burglary in London and further reductions would be harder to come by. The figures also show that there are still proportionately more street searches of black people (79 per 1,000 population) than white people (31 per 1,000 population).  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
