 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Actress Claudette Colbert dies at 92</TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Actress Claudette Colbert dies at 92</b><br><br><br><b><h2>  19 July 1996</h2></b><br><h2> Actress Claudette Colbert dies at 92  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Nick Varley</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>Actress Claudette Colbert, star of such classic 1930s films as It Happened One Night and Cleopatra, died in Barbados yesterday aged 92. The Oscar winner, well-known for her trademark hair bangs and radiant smile, appeared in more than 60 films.  <p>  <p>Comedy was considered her forte - and her comic performance with Clark Gable in It Happened One Night crowned her career. Both stars, as well as director Frank Capra, won Oscars in a then-unprecedented sweep.  <p>  <p>Film critic Pauline Kael said the film "made audiences happy in a way that only a few films in each era do".  <p>  <p>"In the mid-thirties, the Colbert and Gable of this film became Americans' idealized view of themselves - breezy, likeable, sexy, gallant, and maybe just a little harebrained. It was the 'Annie Hall' of its day - before the invention of anxiety."  <p>  <p>Colbert, who had an ocean-front home in Barbados, was born in Paris in 1903. Three years later her father took the family to New York.  <p>  <p>After she graduated from high school, Lily Cauchoin, as she was christened, got a bit part on Broadway and two years later she began her ascent under her new name.  <p>  <p>At the peak of her popularity in the 1930s, Colbert earned $150,000 a picture - a huge sum at the time. But she claimed she was not over ambitious. "I never thought of my career as the primary thing in my life. I looked upon acting as a job, and now, frankly, I regret it," she said at age 77. "I think of all the things I could have done. I just let parts come to me. I never went after them."  <p>  <p>She considered comedy her greatest strength: "I love to play comedy and I can say immodestly that I'm a very good comedienne. But I was always fighting that image, too. I just never had the luck to play bitches." Her chance to act against type came when she was cast to play Margo Channing, the ageing Broadway star in All About Eve, but she injured her back and had to withdraw. The part went to Bette Davis.  <p>  <p>She married twice - the second time for 33 years, until his death, to surgeon Joel Pressman - but had no children.  <p>  <p>In 1991 she told an interviewer she had turned down a number of offers to write a tell-all memoir: "What am I going to say? I married a wonderful doctor, and I was very happy. Period."  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
