 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Robert Collins, keyboard player in the Charlatans killed in car  crash </TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Robert Collins, keyboard player in the Charlatans killed in car crash </b><br><br><br><b><h2>24  July 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Controversial keyboard player from Britpop group killed in car accident   </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Stuart Millar</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>Police were last night investigating the cause of a car crash in which the keyboard player of the  Britpop group the Charlatans was killed. Robert Collins, aged 32, died on Monday night on his way to  hospital after losing control of his red BMW in Monmouth, Gwent.  <p>  <p>A Gwent police spokeswoman said the BMW hit several parked cars before ending up in a field. No  other vehicle was involved, and the cause of the crash is not yet known. A male passenger, aged 31,  who is not being named, escaped unhurt but was in shock, police said.  <p>  <p>A spokesman for the band's record company, Beggar's Banquet, said yesterday: "We are very upset,  not just for Rob's family and his fans, but for the rest of the band."  <p>  <p>The Charlatans were in Monmouth recording their fifth album and were due to go on tour later this  month as special guests of Oasis.  <p>  <p>Collins, from Walsall, West Midlands, supplied the band's trademark swirling Hammond organ sound  which helped the Charlatans to two number one albums. Born out of the Madchester scene in 1990, their  debut album, 'Some Friendly', then went straight to number one for 17 weeks.  <p>  <p>Collins was equally famous for his exploits off-stage. He was jailed in 1993 for driving a getaway  car after a bungled armed robbery.  <p>  <p>His mother, Maureen, said yesterday: "I'm still far too upset to talk."   <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0   SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
