 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Diana's media aide, Jane Atkinson quits six months before end  of contract </TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Diana's media aide, Jane Atkinson, quits six months before end of contract </b><br><br><br><b><h2>24  July 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Diana's media aide quits with six months of contract to run  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Nick Varley</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>The Princess of Wales was left bereft of senior advisers last night after her key media aide  resigned, six months before the end of her contract. Jane Atkinson, who runs her own public relations  consultancy, took up the post in January after Geoff Crawford resigned as the princess's press officer  over her controversial 'Panorama' interview two months earlier. The job will be left vacant. A statement  from Kensington Palace said the princess "has decided there is no longer a requirement for an external  media adviser".  <p>  <p>It means she has lost her two closest advisers. Her private secretary, Patrick Jephson, quit in  January, reportedly furious he was not consulted about the 'Panorama' interview.  <p>  <p>The announcement said the princess had accepted Ms Atkinson's resignation "due to the reduction in  her work commitment" with immediate effect. Ms Atkinson was unavailable for comment.  <p>  <p>Diana quit as patron of almost 100 charities last week, in an episode said to have resulted in the  latest clash between the two. The princess reportedly blamed Ms Atkinson, aged 48, for the negative  reaction to the resignations.  <p>  <p>A critical response to the princess watching heart surgeon Sir Magdi Yacoub at work was also pinned  on Ms Atkinson. She was not consulted about it beforehand.  <p>  <p>Media inquiries will now be dealt with by the remaining three secretaries who run the princess's  office.  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0   SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
