 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Sir Edward Heath paid to speak at Moonie conference</TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Sir Edward Heath paid to speak at Moonie conference</b><br><br><br><b><h2>31 July 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Heath paid to speak at 'Moonie' conference  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Owen Bowcott</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>The former Prime Minister, Sir Edward Heath, will fulfil a fee-paying speaking engagement at a conference in Washington today organised by the Unification Church, whose leader, the Reverend Sun Myung Moon, is banned from entering Britain.  <p>  <p>The three-day meeting, held under the banner of the Family Federation for World Peace, has attracted a galaxy of world leaders, including former US presidents George Bush and Gerald Ford.  <p>  <p>It is the third time that Sir Edward has spoken at international conferences promoted by the Unification Church, otherwise known as the 'Moonie' cult founded by the 76-year-old self-proclaimed Messiah from Korea. At least one other senior British politician has been a guest speaker at one of the church's conferences this year. The former Labour Foreign Secretary, Lord Healey, flew to Japan in June, it was disclosed yesterday, to address the Federation of Island Commonwealths for World Peace. George Robertson, a Unification Church spokesman in London, yesterday confirmed the federation was part of its movement. He declined to discuss the speaking fees involved, which in the past have been described as 'substantial'.  <p>  <p>In October last year the Home Secretary, Michael Howard, banned the Rev Moon from entering Britain on the grounds that his presence was not 'conducive to the public good'.  <p>  <p>The Rev Moon's organisation lost a libel case in 1981 against the Daily Mail which alleged it 'broke up families'. Since being jailed for tax fraud in the United States the following year, he has built a multi-billion pound empire.  <p>  <p>Larry Moffat, an organiser of the Washington conference, yesterday said Sir Edward would talk about the family. "When we are talking about family issues, like poverty, famine, he's one of the most experienced men in the neighbourhood."  <p>  <p>Both Sir Edward and Lord Healey's office said the speaking engagements had been arranged through a speaking 'agency'. Lord Healey was not available for comment but his office in the Lords said they were not sure whether he was aware of the Unification Church connection. Sir Edward, on the way to catch a flight to Washington last night, declined to comment on his fee. "We all know why Michael Howard imposed the ban," he said. "He wanted to get some votes. It was wrong to ban (the Rev Moon). This is an international conference. What we are discussing is the influence that families can have on world affairs after the millennium. This is the same as John Major's Back to Basics."  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 