 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Rioch dismissed two weeks after signing contract as Arsenal manager </TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Rioch dismissed two weeks after signing contract as Arsenal manager  </b><br><br><br><b><h2>1 August 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Rioch signs for Arsenal after 14-month  delay  </h2>
  <br><br>      <p>The Arsenal manager Bruce Rioch last night announced that he had signed a contract with the club,  almost 14 months after arriving at Highbury from Bolton Wanderers.  <p>  <p>Rioch would not declare for how long he had committed himself but said: "I am now waiting for the  club to counter-sign the document."  <p>  <p>Rioch, speaking in Glasgow after seeing Simon Donnelly and Phil O'Donnell hit late goals to give  Celtic a 2-1 win over Arsenal, for whom John Hartson scored, added that he hoped to sign two players  before the 15 August deadline for the Uefa Cup first round.  <p>  <p>Singapore was disappointed to discover that Alan Shearer would not be making his bow for Newcastle  against a local select XI in tonight's friendly, although the England centre-forward met and trained  with his new team-mates in the city-state yesterday.  <p>  <p>Newcastle's manager Kevin Keegan said he wanted to give Shearer time to settle in. "There's  certainly no chance of him playing... I would say Japan [Sunday's friendly] will come too quick [as  well]. It would be very amateurish of me, even if he wanted to, to let him play.  <p>  <p>"It looks like his first game will be the Charity Shield against Manchester United [on Sunday  week]. We are going to Lincoln before that, but that's what it looks like at this stage."  <p>  <p>Keegan, whose team had come back to beat Thailand 2-1 in Bangkok, Faustino Asprilla and Robert Lee  scoring the goals, was reluctant to elaborate on his &#163;15m signing, saying only that Shearer would  appear at a Tyneside news conference on Tuesday. "He has signed for the people of Newcastle. This is really  something we should do back in Newcastle." West Ham lost 3-2 to Torquay United, the bottom club in  last season's Third Division, and the Londoners' &#163;1.5m signing Florin Raducioiu appeared to take  a punch from Jon Gittens. Raducioiu walked off with a swollen cheekbone and Torquay immediately  substituted Gittens. The West Ham manager Harry Redknapp later said he would be reporting the Torquay  player to the FA.  <p>  <p>The former Torquay captain John Uzzell, whose career was cut short by a horrific facial injury  sustained during a match against Brentford five years ago, is suing the London club and Gary Blissett,  the player allegedly involved in the incident.  <p>  <p>At Molineux a crowd of 23,942 attended a testimonial for the popular Wolves full-back Andy Thompson  but Dennis Wise gave Chelsea a 1-0 victory with a 65th-minute penalty. Wise converted after Mark  Hughes, who had earlier hit the post, was brought down in the box.  <p>  <p>Chelsea were again without the injured Gianluca Vialli as well as the player-manager Ruud Gullit.  <p>  <p>In the San Siro last night Internazionale, fielding four newly signed foreign stars,  strolled through a friendly with the English double winners Manchester United and won 3-0.  <p>  <p>Duncan Ferguson and Andrei Kanchelskis were on target as Everton defeated Tranmere 2-1 at Prenton  Park to lift the Liverpool Senior Cup. Kenny Irons scored a late consolation for Rovers.  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0   SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
