 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Belgium buries the two eight-year-old victims of a paedophile  gang with the ceremony of a state funeral </TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Belgium buries the two eight-year-old victims of a paedophile gang </b><br><br><br><b><h2>23 August 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Belgium mourns dead girls  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Stephen Bates</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>Belgium buried the two little girl victims of a paedophile gang in Liege yesterday with all the  pomp and emotion of a state funeral.  <p>  <p>Melissa Russo and Julie Lejeune, both aged eight, were buried as they had lived and as they had  died, side by side, at a private service in the village cemetery at Mons-lez-Liege near their homes  just outside the city. But they were carried there only after a memorial service, televised live, had  unleashed a new wave of national grief. It came at the end of a week in which the discovery of their  deaths at the hands of a group of paedophiles has convulsed Belgium with shock and recrimination.  <p>  <p>Two fire engines and 14 hearses laden with flowers and wreaths preceded the two hearses bearing the  children's bodies. People wept as their small, white coffins were carried into the gothic basilica of  St Martin, on a hillside overlooking Liege.  <p>  <p>Many clutched the composite photograph of the two little girls, used during the long search for  them. Now, below the pictures of their bright optimistic faces, ran the words: "We were only eight,  with lots of dreams. We thought life would be beautiful. You grown-ups, build us a better world." At  the church door, among the mountainous bouquets of lilies, roses and irises, lying next to the posies  and single flowers left by local children and their parents was a wreath from King Albert and his  wife, Queen Paola. Many businesses and shops in the city closed for the morning as a mark of respect  and the government asked people across the country to observe a minute's silence.  <p>  <p>The two children were abducted 15 months ago and were discovered last Sunday buried in the back  garden of Marc Dutroux, a builder and convicted sex offender, in Charleroi 60 miles away. They  apparently starved to death in the spring, hidden in the cellar while he was detained by police for  four months on unrelated theft charges.  <p>  <p>The discovery of their bodies and the rescue of two teenage girls from the cellar have revived the  hunt for missing children in Belgium and aroused fears that Dutroux, his wife and two other men, who  have been charged with him, may be part of a ring of sex offenders trading in abducted children.  Several thousand people crowded outside the church, waiting patiently for hours to pay their respects.  Valerie Delhain, cradling her 15-month-old son Julian, said she had arrived more than two hours before  the service. "I think it is important to show solidarity as a mother. It is just so very sad," she  said.  <p>  <p>Yvan Augeraux held his three-year-old son Jools tightly. "It is important to be here. It is as if  the whole city has died. It is a tragedy." There was sympathetic clapping for the parents of An  Marchal, who disappeared a year ago and is one of the teenagers still missing, and for the children of  the village where Julie and Melissa lived.  <p>  <p>The parents of Julie and Melissa, their faces taut with grief, clutched their sons as they walked  into the church past an honour guard of weeping local firemen. The girls' mothers wore white as a sign  of hope and purity. After the 90-minute service, Stefaan de Clerck, the justice minister representing  the government, was one of the first to leave. He was booed and hissed.  <p>  <p>The last to leave were the parents, fathers hand in hand. Outside they embraced Paul Marchal, An's  father - three men, for two of whom all hope has faded while for the third it flickers dimly on.  <p>  <p>* A fifth person has been arrested in connection with the suspected paedophile ring, the public  prosecutor, Michel Bourlet, said last night. He also said police were studying videotapes they have  found of Dutroux and accomplices with unidentified children.  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0   SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
