 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Liam Gallagher pulls out of Oasis US tour to go househunting with fianc&#233;e </TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Liam Gallagher pulls out of Oasis US tour to go househunting with fianc&#233;e </b><br><br><br><b><h2>30 August 1996</h2></b><br><h2>'No rift' as Oasis singer rejoins tour  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Stuart Millar</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>Oasis singer Liam Gallagher finally set off to rejoin the band on their United States tour yesterday, insisting he would be welcomed by his songwriter brother Noel.  <p>  <p>He left behind his fiancee, Patsy Kensit, who last night denied she was responsible for keeping him in Britain for three extra days. Reports had accused Ms Kensit, aged 28, of making Liam walk out on the band 15 minutes before they were due to depart on Monday, leaving Noel to assume singing duties at the opening concert in Chicago on Tuesday. A statement from Ms Kensit's solicitors said: "Our client wishes to make it clear she did not instruct or in any way seek to persuade Liam Gallagher to withdraw from travelling to America with Oasis."  <p>  <p>Before flying to Chicago, Liam, aged 23, insisted Ms Kensit had nothing to do with his decision to stay in Britain. He also played down reports of a rift between him and Noel. "Me and Noel are all right. We have chats and that and he can't wait to see me," he told GMTV.  <p>  <p>He defended his decision to let the band begin the 14-date tour without him. "Being in a band, you write songs for yourself first. You do your gigs and that after you are settled and happy. I wasn't happy. I didn't have anywhere to live."  <p>  <p>The laryngitis which he claimed stopped him singing at an acoustic set for the music video channel MTV in London last Friday and in Chicago has cleared and he will lead the band for their second date in Michigan tonight. Noel, who sang at the MTV recording and in Chicago, said he would not "give Liam a slap". He added: "We have had enough of slapping each other." MTV may not broadcast the 'Unplugged' acoustic session in the US because Liam pulled out. The channel's executives are said to be considering cancelling Oasis's showcase on the live Video Music Awards in New York next Wednesday.  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
