 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - The Prince and Princess of Wales divorce</TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>The Prince and Princess of Wales divorce</b><br><br><br><b><h2>28 August  1996</h2></b><br><h2>Timetable of Royal divorce  </h2>
  <br><br>      <p>29 July 1981: The wedding of the Prince of Wales and the 20-year-old Lady Diana Spencer in St  Paul's Cathedral: 500,000 people line the streets of London and 650 million worldwide watch on TV.  Honeymoon at Broadlands in Hampshire and on the Royal Yacht Britannia.  <p>  <p>21 June 1982: Prince William is born. Rumours are dismissed that the Princess is suffering from  post-natal depression and anorexia nervosa. But it emerges later that strains are already emerging  over their incompatible interests and friends - particularly the Prince's old women friends.   <p>  <p>15  September 1984: Prince Harry is born. Princess confides to friends that the marriage is in trouble.  Details emerge later of worsening rows and rages, with the Princess becoming more lonely and the  Prince more desperate.   <p>  <p>March 1991: After years of public silences, behind-the-scenes row and holidays  spent apart, the tabloid papers report that the Princess is a close friend of Life Guards officer,  Major James Hewitt.  <p>  <p>June 1992: Diana: Her True Story, by Andrew Morton, reveals that she has suffered from bulimia and  attempted suicide. Tour to India reveals strains in the marriage, with Diana photographed alone before  the Taj Mahal. The couple are dubbed 'The Glums' during tour of Korea.  <p>  <p>August 1992: A tape is published giving details of a telephone conversation between Diana and her  friend James Gilbey: he calls her Squidgy and tells her he loves her and she tells him she doesn't  want to get pregnant.   <p>  <p>9 December 1992: John Major announces in the Commons that the Prince and  Princess are to separate. He says there are no constitutional implications and no reason why the  Princess should not be crowned Queen in due course.   <p>  <p>January 1993: Tape published which is alleged to  be between the Prince and his friend Camilla Parker-Bowles. She calls him darling and he makes  intimate remarks.  <p>  <p>June 1994: In a TV interview with Jonathan Dimbleby, the Prince admits he was unfaithful after the  "irretrievable" breakdown of the marriage.   <p>  <P>November 1995: Diana appears on BBC1's 'Panorama' and admits she was unfaithful with James Hewitt. But she insists she does not want a divorce.  <p>  <p>December 1995: The Queen writes to both the Prince and Princess telling them to seek a divorce. Charles immediately  agrees but says he has no intention of remarrying.  <p>  <p>February 1996: Diana agrees to divorce and negotiations start between lawyers. At one point she  threatens to withdraw because of Charles's alleged unwillingness to agree to her demands.  <p>  <p>15 July 1996: Decree nisi granted after terms are finally agreed. Princess loses title of Her Royal  Highness but gets a lump sum of &#163;17m and &#163;350,000 a year to run her private office.  <p>  <p>19 August 1996: Buckingham Palace floats plans to scrap the &#163;9m Civil List, end the monarch's  role as head of the Church of England, allow woman equal rights of succession, and allow the monarch  to marry a Catholic.   <p>  <p>28 August 1996: Decree absolute ends the 15-year marriage which began as a  fairy tale but became a tabloid soap opera.  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0   SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
