 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Official confirms relationship between Nelson Mandela and Graca Machel</TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Official confirms relationship between Nelson Mandela and Graca Machel</b><br><br><br><b><h2>2 September 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Mandela in love, says official  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Chris McGreal</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>After months of speculation, a spokesman for Nelson Mandela confirmed yesterday that the South African president has a "steady relationship" with Graca Machel, the widow of former Mozambican president, Samora Machel. Parks Mankahlana was responding to a report in a Johannesburg newspaper that Mr Mandela, aged 78, is in love with Mrs Machel, aged 50. "All I can say is, the story is not untrue. But I'm not aware of any marriage plans," Mr Mankahlana said.  <p>  <p>The relationship has been an open secret in South Africa since last year, but speculation was fuelled again two weeks ago when the couple kissed at the wedding of the Zimbabwean president, Robert Mugabe.  <p>  <p>The story, in yesterday's Sunday Independent, quoted sources in the president's African National Congress as saying the couple will take a higher public profile and that Mrs Machel will spend two weeks a month at the president's home.  <p>  <p>There is unlikely to be any serious public objection to the relationship, given the widespread view that Mr Mandela deserves whatever happiness he can find, and general respect for Mrs Machel, who heads a United Nations children's project in South Africa.  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
