 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Australian man first to die by legal euthanasia</TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Australian man first to die by legal euthanasia</b><br><br><br><b><h2>26 September 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Australian is first in world to die using legal euthanasia  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Christopher Zinn</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>A former pilot has used a computer-driven 'death machine' to become the first person in the world to die using legally sanctioned euthanasia, it was revealed today.  <p>  <p>The Northern Territory man, who suffered from prostate cancer and was in his mid-sixties, allowed the machine to pump barbiturates and a muscle relaxant into his bloodstream.  <p>  <p>The Australian, who wished to remain anonymous, was accompanied by Dr Philip Nitschke and two other doctors who signed consent forms.  <p>  <p>His death in Darwin on Sunday has already drawn condemnation from religious leaders and pro-life groups.  <p>  <p>The death by euthanasia is the first under the Northern Territory's Rights of the Terminally Ill Act, which became law 18 months ago.  <p>  <p>It allows a terminally ill patient to ask a doctor to give a lethal injection or provide it for self-administration.  <p>  <p>Dr Nitschke, who pioneered the new act, said: "The patient was suffering from terminal cancer and had asked for assistance under the Act. In consultation with his wife, [he] chose a time and asked for assistance with a lethal injection."  <p>  <p>The man left a detailed letter explaining the reasons for his decision, which is due to be released at a press conference later today. The man's death comes as the legislation faces a challenge from a Federal Private Members Bill. The Act could also be overturned in the High Court in November.  <p>  <p>The head of the Catholic Church in Australia said the first case of euthanasia was a "shameful day for Australia".  <p>  <p>Archbishop Goodhew of the Sydney Anglican diocese said: "It's a very sad thing... [The] consequences may not be known for another 25 years and we may be very sorry."  <p>  <p>And a spokesperson for the Australian Federation of Right to Life Associations commented: "I feel very sad that we are the first nation in the whole world to have voluntary euthanasia."  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
