 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Pope visits France amid controversy on Clovis anniversary </TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Pope visits France amid controversy on Clovis anniversary </b><br><br><br><b><h2>19 September 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Pass Notes - No 889: King Clovis  </h2>
  <br><br>      <p>Age: Merovingian, about 1,530 years old.  <p>  <p>Occupation: King of the Francs. In what could be termed a shotgun baptism, he had himself christened. That convinced all the warring barbarians left behind after the Roman Empire to join together in one happy family called France.  <p>  <p>Appearance: Every 100 years, or whenever France needs to remind herself that she is a great nation - the 'elder daughter of the Church'.  <p>  <p>Clovis had a daughter? No, France is the 'elder daughter' because Clovis arranged for her to be the first western European state to adopt Roman Catholicism.  <p>  <p>Did Clovis have a son then? That's not really the point of this Pass Notes but yes, he had four sons by a couple of wives, including Queen Clotilde. Jean-Marie Le Pen, leader of the National Front, counts himself among them. That Queen Clotilde had a knack for delayed gestation: Mr Le Pen would probably concede that he is a descendant. Anyway, he feels very strongly about being in attendance in Reims on Sunday when the Pope celebrates the 1,500th anniversary of Clovis's baptism.  <p>  <p>Don't tell me, someone has dug up a family tree and Mr Le Pen is not related to Clovis: Actually no. Fifth century records are a bit vague which has allowed Mr Le Pen to make all sorts of remarks about the purity of the French race.  <p>  <p>That must be a bit embarrassing for the Pope: If he is conscious, yes. All that is known is that John Paul II has appendicitis but is determined to go to Reims anyway.  <p>  <p>You might call it ap-Pendicitis! Ha-ha. In fact, the two men seem to be broadly in agreement about condoms, abortion and the dozens of other topics which are inspiring anti-Pope demonstrations throughout France this week. What about Clovis's views on condoms? They are not known. What historians have managed to ascertain, however, is that he may not have been baptised in Reims after all, certainly not on 22 September and probably not in 496. When then? Christmas time 498 AD, along with 3,000 of his soldiers. In that case, I know what Clovis would be most likely to say - "Let's march on Rome": No, that was Umberto Bossi, the leader of the Italian Northern League, in Monday's Pass Notes. King Clovis would be more likely to say: "Capital - we'll put it right here." He decided that Paris should be the capital of France, you see.  <p>  <p>And least likely to say? "Let's march on Rome."  <p>  <p>Not to be confused with: Umberto Bossi, Joan of Arc, Asterix, Elvis.   <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
