 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Claudia Schiffer retires at 26</TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Claudia Schiffer retires at 26</b><br><br><br><b><h2>20 September 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Supermodel retires at 26</h2><h3>How big name with a dated look reached sell-by date  </h3>  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Susannah Frankel</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>The supermodel Claudia Schiffer has announced her retirement at the age of 26. Ms Schiffer said yesterday that from now on she would only be making "guest appearances" for top designers such as Versace and Valentino.  <p>  <p>Her move, following the decision of IMG models to lay off more than 60 of their girls aged 27 and over, does not bode well for those in the profession of 'a certain age'.  <p>  <p>But age is not the only thing that suggests Ms Schiffer is past her sell-by date - after all, Stella Tennant, who has taken over from her as the face of Chanel, is also 26.  <p>  <p>The real reason for Ms Schiffer's premature retirement is more likely to be that, when seen alongside the more idiosyncratic, so-called 'real' good looks of the new wave of models (Ms Tennant, Kate Moss, Trish Goff, and Esther de Jong), her appeal seems sadly dated - as, indeed, does that of her contemporaries Linda Evangelista, aged 30, Cindy Crawford, also 30, and Naomi Campbell, 26.  <p>  <p>Only last year, Jean Paul Gaultier advised Ms Schiffer to "get a new haircut - people are really growing bored of this blonde mane."  <p>  <p>On hearing of the retirement of his muse, designer Karl Lagerfeld said he wished a time machine could transport her back to the silent film era. "She would have been a wonderful Hollywood silent star. Claudia is part of another world, another fashion, another spirit, another time." Now, he said, she would be "better off doing promotions".  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
