 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Clashes between Israelis and Palestinians after tunnel opens in Jerusalem </TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Clashes between Israelis and Palestinians after tunnel opens in Jerusalem </b><br><br><br><b><h2>25 September 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Jerusalem tunnel protest  </h2>
  <br><br>      The Palestinian Authority yesterday called for demonstrations throughout the West Bank, Gaza Strip and Jerusalem to protest against Israel's extension of an archaeological tunnel which runs the length of the Al Aqsa mosque, the third-holiest site in Islam.  <p>  <p>"It will not be a strike but a suspension of work at noon in all Palestinian areas tomorrow in order for there to be marches," Hanan Ashrawi, the authority's minister of higher education, said after an emergency cabinet meeting in Gaza.  <p>  <p>The cabinet decision came shortly after the Palestine Liberation Organisation called on the United Nations Security Council to reverse Israel's action, which further asserts its claim to the whole of Jerusalem, The Palestinian Authority president, Yasser Arafat, said the work - carried out after midnight under heavy police protection - was a "big crime against our religious and holy places".  <p>  <p>Police said they fired rubber bullets to disperse youths throwing stones and bottles (and setting vehicles alight) during the work. They said 11 Palestinians were arrested.  <p>  <p>The Israeli prime minister, Binyamin Netanyahu, said in London he was "very proud" they were implementing the decision to extend the tunnel.  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
