 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Bob Geldof fights for custody of his children after drugs raid at Paula's house </TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Bob Geldof fights for custody of his children after drugs raid at Paula's house </b><br><br><br><b><h2>27 September 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Geldof fights for children after raid  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Nick Varley</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>The Live Aid founder Bob Geldof last night launched a High Court custody battle against his ex-wife Paula Yates over the couple's three children. The rock star's application came after drugs squad officers raided the home in London that Ms Yates shares with her new partner, Michael Hutchence, lead singer of the group INXS.  <p>  <p>Reports suggested drugs squad officers had seized what they suspected was opium, but police would only confirm that 'substances' had been removed. Ms Yates, aged 34, and Mr Hutchence, 36, are in Australia with their two-month-old daughter, Heavenly Hiraani.  <p>  <p>Mr Geldof, 41, is thought to have made an application for Fifi Trixibelle, 13, Peaches, six, and Pixie, four, to live with him at his Kent home. The three children live with their mother and Mr Hutchence in Chelsea, but are staying with their father while the couple are away.  <p>  <p>Mr Geldof, now a millionaire through his television production company Planet 24, appeared before a judge in chambers, Mrs Justice Hale, at the High Court yesterday evening. He launched an emergency action in the Family Division after learning of the police raid. It is understood he won a temporary order, lasting one week.  <p>  <p>However, Mark Stephens, Ms Yates and Mr Hutchence's lawyer, said he was "mystified" by news of Mr Geldof's legal move and described any order as "unwarranted and inappropriate".  <p>  <p>He added: "It all seems to be happening while Paula and Michael are 10,000 miles away. I'm mystified by this and will be making inquiries of Mr Geldof's lawyers as to what is happening."  <p>  <p>Mr Stephens said Ms Yates and Mr Hutchence were in "complete surprise" following the raid on their home. The couple had received no contact of any kind from the police, he added.  <p>  <p>Their nanny, Anita Debney, was questioned by police following the raid. According to reports last night, she has resigned after 12 years. The couple are due to fly home today, and police have indicated they will interview them when they return.  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
