 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Madonna gives birth to  daughter</TITLE></HEAD> <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000"  alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea"> <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG  SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br>
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Madonna gives birth to  daughter</b><br><br><br><b><h2>16 October 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Pass  Notes - No 904: Madonna Junior  </h2>
 <br><br><br>      <p>Full name: Lourdes Maria Ciccone Leon. <p> <p>Age: One day. <p> <p>Appearance:  Heavenly. <p> <p>Conception: Immaculate. <p> <p>Birthplace: Bethlehem. <p> <p>You  jest: Of course. It was the Good Samaritan Hospital, Los Angeles. Weight: 6lb  9oz. <p> <p>Gory details: Three-hour labour, followed by Caesarean section.  Mother: A well-known Catholic. <p> <p>Father: A fit young fellow co-opted for the  purpose. The couple are not married. <p> <p>Why has the birth caused such  consternation? Something to do with a star. Followers of the star: Wise men from  media organisations around the world who reckon they can cash in on the birth of  the decade. Tabloid editors said they had "stormtroopers" in place ready to  pierce the high-level security at the hospital. <p> <p>And did they? No, Madonna  is one smart cookie. <p> <p>Who played Gabriel? The unlikely figure of Heidi  Fleiss's father, Dr Paul Fleiss, Hollywood's guardian angel, who oversaw the  birth. <p> <p>And God? Charlton Heston is auditioning. <p> <p>An impromptu carol  to mark the occasion: While shepherds watched MTV by night, etc, etc <p>  <p>Useful gifts for the mother: Gold, frankincense, myrrh (or platinum) and a  pointy maternity bra, preferably made by Christian Lacroix. <p> <p>Madonna's  poetic description of seeing the babe during pregnancy: "I was stunned when I saw  on the ultrasound a tiny, living creature spinning around in my womb.  Tap-dancing, I think. Waving its tiny arms around and trying to suck its thumb. I  could have sworn I heard it laughing." <p> <p>Why should it be laughing? Have you  seen Madonna's bank balance? Peculiar admission by a spokesperson: "Madonna was  closely involved during her pregnancy." <p> <p>Not to be confused with: Lord's  cricket ground (a holy place). Not under any circumstances to be confused with:  Heavenly Hiraani Tigerlily, Fifi Trixibelle, Peaches Honeyblossom or Little  Pixie. <p> <p>Do say: "Ring out you crystal spheres / Once bless our human ears /  (If ye have powers to touch our senses so) / And let your silver chime / Move in  melodious time" (Milton, 'On the Morning of Christ's Nativity'). Don't say: "What  do you do for an encore?" <p> <p>Oh, by the way, why have you used such a useless  picture? Pix of the pregnant Madonna were free; bidding for snaps of the baby  started at $1m. <p> <p> <p> <p> <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr> <td  width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif"  ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG  SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A  HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG  SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A  HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG  SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A  HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG  SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A  HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG  SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A  HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG  SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr> <td  align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG  border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td> <td align=center valign=middle  width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html