 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Sarah Holt and Sarah Bird jailed for  refusing to testify against violent man </TITLE></HEAD> <body bgcolor="#ffffff"  text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea"> <A  HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br>
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Sarah Holt and Sarah Bird  jailed for refusing to testify against violent man </b><br><br><br><b><h2>19  October 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Terrified 'victims' appeal over  jailing</h2><h3>Women who feared reprisals turn to High Court  </h2>
 <br>By 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Alan Watkins</b><br><br>      <p> <p>Two young women jailed for contempt of court after refusing to give  evidence against a man accused of grievous bodily harm, because they feared  reprisals if they did so, are to have an appeal heard in the High Court next  week. Sarah Holt, aged 20, from Waltham Abbey, Essex, was jailed for three months  at Chelmsford crown court for refusing to go into the witness box against her  former boyfriend Alex Fryatt. Her friend Sophie Bird, 22, was jailed for two  months after she too told the court she no longer wished to give evidence. <p>  <p>As a result the case against Mr Fryatt collapsed and proceedings were dropped.  <p> <p>The judge, Mr Justice Benjamin Pearson, refused an immediate appeal  certificate but yesterday solicitors acting for the girls said they were  confident that the High Court would soon hear their appeal. <p> <p>Both women  were sent to Holloway prison and were said yesterday by angry relatives to be  "deeply distressed and upset" at the sentence. Both claim that after Mr Fryatt  was arrested for allegedly attacking Sarah and causing a broken jaw and other  injuries, threats were made of reprisals if they went into the witness box. <p>  <p>Sarah's father, David, said yesterday that to jail girls who were simply  scared was "complete and utter madness". <p> <p>He said it must have been obvious  to the judge that the pair were frightened for their lives as a result of a  campaign of threats. <p> <p>Mr Holt said last night that the appeal of the two  women could be heard as soon as Monday. <p> <p>He also revealed that Sarah had  been transferred to Drake Hall open prison, Staffordshire, although Sophie  remains in Holloway. <p> <p>Julie Bindel, of the International Conference on  Violence, Abuse and Women's Citizenship, said yesterday that she believed a  "dreadful miscarriage of justice" had taken place. <p> <p>She said both women  were clearly trying to protect themselves. They should be released immediately  and given the support that they need. "This is a subject which everyone, from  police to judges, needs to understand much more about. To put these girls into  prison because of their own fear is an outrage," she said. <p> <p> <p> <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr> <td width=40><A  HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG  SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A  HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG  SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A  HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG  SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A  HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG  SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A  HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG  SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A  HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG  SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr> <td  align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG  border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td> <td align=center valign=middle  width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td> <td align=right valign=middle  width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0   SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td> </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
