 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Matthew Harding dies in helicopter crash</TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Matthew Harding dies in helicopter crash</b><br><br><br><b><h2>25 October 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Harding crash investigators hunt for clues  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>David Ward</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>Air accident investigators are to examine the wreckage of the helicopter in which the vice-chairman of Chelsea Football Club, Matthew Harding, and four others died on Tuesday night.  <p>  <p>The debris from the Cheshire crash site will be analysed in a hangar at Farnborough, the Hampshire headquarters of the Department of Transport's Air Accidents Investigation Branch. A report is expected within about six months.  <p>  <p>The Twin Squirrel helicopter took off for Heathrow from a Bolton car park following Chelsea's 2-1 defeat by Bolton Wanderers in a Coca-Cola Cup game. It plunged into a field near Middlewich about half an hour later and burst into flames.  <p>  <p>Two investigators have been in Cheshire since the crash but they have given no indication of possible causes. One problem they face is that small helicopters do not carry black box voice recorders.  <p>  <p>The Cheshire coroner, John Hibbert, yesterday formally opened and adjourned inquests on Mr Harding, aged 42, his three friends Tony Burridge, aged 39, Raymond Deane, 43, and John Bauldie, 47, and the pilot, Michael Goss, aged 38. All five died of multiple injuries.  <p>  <p>He is expected to await the findings of the accident investigation team before holding a full hearing. The men's bodies have now been released to their families.  <p>  <p>At Stamford Bridge, Chelsea's ground, grieving fans continued to arrive to lay flowers, shirts and scarves in memory of Mr Harding. A memorial wall stretched for more than 100ft inside the main gates of the ground. There were also tributes from supporters of many other clubs including Liverpool, West Ham, Manchester United, Queens Park Rangers, Sheffield United and Tottenham, who Chelsea play on Saturday.  <p>  <p>Richard Lewington, one of a family of seven from Carshalton, Surrey, said: "We have brought tributes of flowers, scarves and shirts to pay our respects to Matthew Harding, who was Mr Chelsea, a great bloke, a true fan and one of us."  <p>  <p>Chelsea players arriving for training drove straight into their training ground at the Imperial College sports ground in Harlington, west London, without speaking to waiting journalists.  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.