<HEAD> <TITLE>Willetts to get &#163;8,000 pay-off</TITLE> </HEAD>


<BODY bgcolor="#ffffff">

<table width=580 border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0> <TR> <td width=100> <font
size="-1">Friday<BR>13 December<BR> 1996</font> </td> <TD align=right> <IMG
SRC="pix/gdn200.gif" >

</td> </tr>

<tr> <td colspan=2 valign=bottom > <img width=580 height=1 src="pix/dot.gif">
</td> </tr> </table>

<table width=580 border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0> 
<tr> <td width=100
valign=top ><BR><B>Corruption in the Commons</b> <img width=100 height=1 src="pix/dot.gif">

<FONT SIZE="3"><A HREF="131296/banker.html"><img src="pix/arrow.gif" border=0 height=15
width=15 ></A> Banker picked in whips shuffle</font> <img width=100 height=1 src="pix/dot.gif">

<FONT SIZE="3"><A HREF="121296/index.html"><img src="pix/arrow.gif"
border=0 height=15 width=15 ></A>Thursday<br>12 December</font><font size=2><br><br><img
