	<td valign=top> <IMG valign=top SRC="pix/debate.gif">
</td>
</tr>
	


<TR><TD  height=110 valign=middle width=580 colspan=4><FONT  SIZE="4" COLOR="#ffffff">
<b>The Guardian's education debates are being staged to open
up the big issues to the widest possible discussion by students, parents,
teachers and other concerned citizens - in the paper, at live events at the
University of London's Institute of Education and through the Guardian's
website. Read the arguments and join the debates on selection, university
tuition fees, teacher bashing and the controversial inspection regime at
Ofsted.</b></font><br>
</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE><BR clear=all>
