</TR>

<TR>
<TD align=center valign=middle height=60 width=290>
<FONT SIZE="4" COLOR="#FFFFFF"> <b>Debate 1: <A HREF="debate1.html"> Selection</a><br>
Do we need a greater degree of selection in compulsory education?</b></font></td>

<TD align=center valign=middle height=60 width=290><FONT SIZE="4" COLOR="#FFFFFF"><b>Debate 2: <A HREF="debate2.html">University tuition fees </a><br>
Can universities thrive without charging tuition fees for all graduates?</b>
</font></td>  </tr>

<TR>
<TD align=center valign=top height=60 width=290><FONT SIZE="4" COLOR="#FFFFFF"><b>Debate 3: <A HREF="debate3.html">The professionalism of teachers </a><br>
Does questioning the professionalism of teachers do more harm than good?
</b></font></td> 
<!--Debate 4-->
	<td align=center height=60 valign=top> <FONT  SIZE="4" COLOR="#FFFFFF"><b>Debate 4: <A HREF="debate4.html">Inspections and league tables</a><br>
