<HTML>

<HEAD>
<TITLE>The Guardian Education</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF" TEXT="333333" LINK="660000" VLINK="336699">
<P><BR>
<!--TOP-->
<TABLE BORDER="0" CELLPADDING="0" CELLSPACING="0" WIDTH="550">
<TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER><IMG SRC="pix/edition.gif" ALT="First Edition" BORDER="0"></TD></TR>
</TABLE>

<P><br>
<!-- COPY-->

<TABLE BORDER="0" CELLPADDING="10" CELLSPACING="0" WIDTH="550">
<TR><TD VALIGN=TOP>

An invaluable resource for teachers and parents wanting an accessible way of explaining the stories behind the news. These articles are prepared in association with the First Edition current affairs series for schools on Channel 4, presented by Jon Snow and transmitted every Tuesday morning at 11.45am and repeated on Wednesday at 11.45am and Saturday at 7.45am. Every week you can win £100 for your school in the First Edition Quiz. Visit the <A HREF="http://www.channel4.com/schools" TARGET="_new">Channel 4 </A> website for details.<P></TD>


	<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=CENTER>
	<IMG SRC="pix/jonsnow.jpeg" ALT="Jon Snow" WIDTH="60" HEIGHT="86" BORDER="0"><BR><FONT SIZE="1">Jon Snow</FONT>
	</TD>
</TR>
	
<TR>
	<TD COLSPAN=2>
	<UL TYPE=SQUARE>
	<LI><A HREF="war.html"><I>11 February 1997</I></A><BR>
