<TR>
	<TD ALIGN=LEFT><h2>Watch this space</h2></TD>

</TR>
<TR>
	<TD>Instead of telling students what they are meant to be interested in, every week this page will contain a collection of articles submitted from campus publications around the country, with illustrations commissioned from art students. We&#146;ll consider local news stories, creative writing and humour.<p>Submissions wanted: Contact Emily Sheffield, who compiles 
the page, via <A HREF="mailto:student@guardian.co.uk">e-mail</A>, fax 0171-713 4366 or post at: Guardian Education, 119 Farringdon 
Road, London ECIR 3ER. Please include your place of education and contact number.</TD>

</TR>

