<HEAD>
<TITLE>Observatorium - The Exhibit Hall</TITLE>

<META name="description" content=
	"The Observatorium Exhibit Hall uses satellite images and easy
to understand narrative to introduce and explain concepts in earth and
space science.  New exhibits are added about once a month.">

<META name="keywords" content=
	"exhibit hall, space exhibit, science exhibit, space science
exhibit, earth science exhibit, museum, NASA IITA">

