<P>For more information about RSPAC</A>, send e-mail to 
<A HREF="mailto:curator@rspac.ivv.nasa.gov">curator@rspac.ivv.nasa.gov</A>
To make comments or suggestions regarding the Observatorium, send e-mail 
to the Observatorium Curator at 
<A HREF="mailto:curator@rspac.ivv.nasa.gov">curator@rspac.ivv.nasa.gov
</A>.</P>

<P>Our US postal address is:</P>

<address>RSPAC - BDM<br>
WVU/NASA Software IV&V Center<br>
100 University Drive<br>
Fairmont, WV 26554<br>
</address>

<P>Phone: <I>(304)367-8331</I></P>
<P>Fax: <I>(304)367-8211</I></P>
<BR><BR>

<p> Visit the <a href="/cgi-bin/log.pl?http://www.ivv.nasa.gov">NASA/WVU Software IV&V
Facility</A> in Fairmont, West Virginia, our host facility.</p>

