<H2>Emergency Preparedness and Response</H2>
</CENTER>

<P>
Emergency preparedness, planning, and mitigation are critical in the 
face of natural and technological disasters. Remote sensing data is being 
used in the prediction of potential emergency and crisis situations, and 
in the handling of these situations should they occur.
</P>
<P>
Here are some resources focused on predicting and assisting in emergency 
and crisis situations.</P>
