<H2>Land Management and Land Use Planning</H2>
</CENTER>

<P>Land management and land use planning involve activities like
environmental impact reporting, hazardous materials management,
utility planning and maintenance, traffic congestion management,
commercial marketing and land development.  Remote sensing data has
many applications in these areas for local and regional planners,
government agencies, and commercial interests.  </P>

<P>The projects cited below show how data and tools are being integrated
in support of land management and land use planning.</P>

