<H2>Internet Connectivity</H2>
</CENTER>


<P>Much has been said and written about the Internet and its promise of
improved entertainment, education, and social and political discourse. 
For Internet to fulfill its promise (and hype), it must be accessible,
economical, and easy to use.</P>

